00:06:41,068 --> 00:06:43,136 line:-2
[Luming]
Thanks, Yongjun!


131
00:06:43.170 --> 00:06:45.405 line:-2 align:center
As Yongjun mentioned
in the talk,


132
00:06:45,439 --> 00:06:47,674 line:-2
you can now configure
the meta tag


133
00:06:47,708 --> 00:06:51,245 line:-2
